    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03745.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden NJ</name>
                    <date when="1885-08-15">
                        <hi rend="underline">8.15.85</hi></date>
                    <date when="1885-08-15">
                        <hi rend="underline">8 PM</hi></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Walt,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p> I send you a fish caught at "Anglesea"<ptr target="loc.03745_n4"/> at 2 PM <hi rend="underline">today</hi> by
                Harned &amp; myself.<ptr target="loc.03745_n1"/> We have just arrived home after a
                good time, <hi rend="underline">although</hi> I got <hi rend="underline"
                    >knocked</hi> off <hi rend="underline">the boat</hi>&#8212;struck <pb xml:id="leaf002r"
                    facs="loc.03745.003_large.jpg" type="recto"/> over the head with the
                "boom"&#8212;and knocked over into <hi rend="underline">twelve feet</hi> water&#8212;whence I had to swim ashore&#8212;of course it all ended well&#8212;and all's well that <hi rend="underline">ends
                well</hi> although I got an awful blow between the eye. I go early in the morning
                (Sunday) to see Mary&#8212;my wife at <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#nhg" cert="low">Atlantic</unclear>&#8212;but Monday will
                see you at <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#nhg" cert="low">7</unclear>. Expect to be home a good deal next week&#8212;Tom sends <hi rend="underline">Love</hi>.
                Regards to Mrs Davis<ptr target="n6113"/></p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Tenderly</salute>
                <signed>JM Scovel</signed>
            </closer>

            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.03745.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <postscript>
                <p> PS One of the "Press" Men came up with us and told me at the train that the
                    <hi rend="underline">Syndicate</hi> article <choice>
                        <abbr>wd</abbr>
                        <expan>would</expan>
                    </choice> be in Sunday's <hi rend="underline">Press</hi>. Ordered the Tribunes
                    for you<ptr target="loc.03745_n3"/>
                </p>
                <signed>&#8212;JMS</signed>
            </postscript>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.03745.004_large.jpg" type="verso"/>

        </body>
